I am rapidly proceeding with the 6th vol of the Fragmenta;
Fascicles 41-47 (200 pp.) of vol. 6 were published between July 1867 and June 1868. Two further fascicles followed in December 1868 but printing of the index was delayed and bound volumes were not issued until August 1869 (B69.08.01). the 5th
B67.02.07. will have been received by you through your excellent Consul, the General Latham, who with his family occasionally honors me with his visit.
